Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.22,Show_Title,Screen,0,0,0,,{\c&H0200E9&\3c&H000000&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:22.65,Show_Title,Screen,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,650)\c&H2E2C2C&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs12\c&HF3F3F3&\bord0\alpha&HFF&\t(237,736,1 \alpha&H00&)}The Culling Game Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:19.66,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So, is Mai-chan dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.34,Main,MakiMother,0,0,0,,It's the clan head you \Nshould be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.81,Main,MakiMother,0,0,0,,Besides, the one who's nearly dead is Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.78,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,That so? Good thing, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.58,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Maki-chan's a real beauty, but she's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.77,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,She can't support a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.76,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Any woman who can't walk \Nhumbly behind her man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.02,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,deserves to be stabbed \Nin the back and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.67,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mai-chan's a great woman in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.82,Sign_Basic,Screen,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,310)\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\shad0\c&HCECDD1&}Special First-Grade Sorcerer    Naoya Zen'in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.65,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,She has the same face and \Nthe same tits as Maki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.47,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,She may put on a brave face,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.70,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,but she understands her place as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.84,Main,Ogi,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.97,Main,Ogi,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.50,Main,Ogi,0,0,0,,Your own father is in critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.06,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:04.11,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But what's it matter if I'm here or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:07.76,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the next head \Nof the Zen'in Clan anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:12.09,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,All my older brothers are knuckleheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.44,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,And Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.11,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,you're his little brother, \Nbut you're lackluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.44,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Your daughters are out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.43,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,And Jinichi-kun, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.93,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Your looks are no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.77,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Woulda been better if you \Ngot Toji-kun's looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.87,Sign_Basic,Screen,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,315)\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\shad0\c&HCECDD1&}Special First-Grade Sorcerer    Ogi Zen'in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:38.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,315)\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\shad0\c&HCECDD1&}Special First-Grade Sorcerer    Jinichi Zen'in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.09,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{\an8}Papa's in critical condition, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.91,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.96,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,I see everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.06,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Just now, the head of the Zen'in Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:51.57,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Naobito Zen'in-sama, has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:07:00.15,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,I, Furudate, shall now read his will, \Nwhich he entrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.82,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,It was Naobito-sama's wish that \Nthis will be read by me once
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.02,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Ogi Zen'in-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.69,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Jinichi Zen'in-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.99,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,and Naoya Zen'in-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:16.63,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,were all gathered together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:22.01,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,If there are no objections, \Nthen I shall begin the reading of his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:34.51,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,First, Naoya Zen'in shall be made \Nthe 27th head of the Zen'in Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:40.34,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Second, Naoya shall inherit all \Nthe assets and cursed tools stored
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:44.52,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,in both the Jujutsu High and \Nthe Zen'in Clan's forbidden vaults,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:50.69,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,and Naoya shall require agreement \Nfrom either Ogi Zen'in or Jinichi Zen'in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:54.35,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,to make use of their contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.35,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.60,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.41,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.70,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,in the event that Satoru Gojo has died,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:06.42,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,or otherwise lost the use of his \Nmental faculties for any reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.12,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,then the covenant with \NToji Fushiguro shall be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:13.27,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,Megumi Fushiguro shall be \Nwelcomed into the Zen'in Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.43,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,and that same person shall \Nbecome the head of the Zen'in Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.69,Main,Furudate,0,0,0,,inheriting all of its assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.56,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.47,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.47,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Those two have no balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.76,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,They think having some \Nunknown brat as the head
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.94,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,would be better than me, \Nso they ain't doing jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.33,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Where's Megumi-kun, and \Nwhat's he doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.99,Main,MakiMother,0,0,0,,I don't know much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:40.83,Main,MakiMother,0,0,0,,Only that he's on a mission \Nto find Yuji Itadori in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.04,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.21,Main,MakiMother,0,0,0,,The vessel of Sukuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.92,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Then go tell the big shots
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.95,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,that Naoya Zen'in is gonna \Nkill Sukuna's vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.26,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Megumi-kun is with Sukuna's vessel, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.59,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll kill 'em both together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.47,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Tokyo is pandemonium right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.85,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,People can die anytime for any reason there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.00,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Once I kill him, the rest \Nwill work itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.53,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm the head of the Zen'in Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.65,Flashback,Yuji,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.42,Flashback,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.42,Flashback,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Only me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.85,Flashback,Nanami,0,0,0,,You take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.85,Flashback,Yuji,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.11,Flashback,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.51,Flashback,Nanami,0,0,0,,Itadori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.54,Flashback,Tsukumo,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:54.57,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.91,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,How are your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.60,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,They're fine, other than where \NI took that Black Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.25,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's probably because of Sukuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.44,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,I can feel how his power has grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.03,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.93,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.91,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,You can return to Jujutsu High, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.80,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,I'd like to retrieve the remains\Nof Shoso and the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.71,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.84,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's not even an issue of \Nme wanting to return or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.73,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Sukuna is plotting something \Nthat uses Fushiguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:34.26,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Plus, I've killed so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:38.81,Flashback_Italics,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,What are you going to do when someone \Nyou saved kills someone else in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.10,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,I can't stay with the others anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.77,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,And are you okay with this, Choso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.06,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,I killed your little brothers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.02,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.59,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,That was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.70,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Eso and Kechizu would have \Ndone the same in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.19,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Forgiving you or not doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.75,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.16,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.97,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,For now, we need to reduce \Nthe number of cursed spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.58,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Choso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.83,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.87,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,How terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.53,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,I already sensed he was \Npowerful when we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.45,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,Now he's added subtlety to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.31,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,He has unfaltering control \Nof his cursed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.36,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,and exceptional physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.92,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,He's truly like a war god!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.91,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,That shows he wasn't yet \Nin top shape until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.13,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,You're impressive, my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.97,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.83,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,I'll say it as often as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.97,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Remember back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.63,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,They should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.39,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Your father should have had \Nstitches in his forehead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.63,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Megumi-kun ain't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.52,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Am I the first to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.70,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.74,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,He's way too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.15,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.49,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Was he just talking about Fushiguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.52,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,What are y'all doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.01,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're sticking out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.39,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Not gonna try to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.17,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.86,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,What, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.03,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You've been sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.38,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You lost Satoru-kun's protection, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.38,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.67,Flashback_Italics,Ino,0,0,0,,There are many sorcerers who've been saved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.47,Flashback_Italics,Ino,0,0,0,,due to Gojo-san's influence, \Npride, and whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.03,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,My business is with Megumi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:40.15,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,so to be blunt, I couldn't \Ncare less if you live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.35,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Don't want you running \Naround willy-nilly, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.11,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna break your legs for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.51,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,What do you want with Fushiguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.01,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I need him to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.44,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Though it'd be great for me if he'd \Nwrite a few lines before he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.37,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I heard Megumi-kun's been searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.64,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,He's certainly fast, but something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.65,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,It's probably his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.02,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're doing better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.03,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I honestly underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.98,Italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I know the vessel's got stuff going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.52,Italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,but what's that thing beside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.36,Italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,Guess I'll crank the speed up a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.08,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Gojo-sensei?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.99,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's even creepier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:53.93,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.93,Show_Title,Screen,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,0)\3c&HB0C0B3&\c&H1D201B&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:00.55,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.81,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,Whoever he is, his goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.81,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,What are each of you to Itadori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:09.57,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} here to execute Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.20,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Hold up. I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.58,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're Okkotsu-kun, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.14,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Okkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.30,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,The second-year Fushiguro mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:29.58,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,A special-grade sorcerer, like Gojo-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.83,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.34,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm Naoya Zen'in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.30,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm Maki-chan's cousin,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:37.16,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,and I've been told to kill \NItadori-kun, like you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.13,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,We're running, Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:38.84,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.22,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll stay outta your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.94,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,The blond one's a speed type \Nwith some kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.10,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,We need to avoid getting into a chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.98,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,I'll stall him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.35,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.17,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,In return, once you've killed Itadori-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.14,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,could you hold off on reporting it for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.37,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I want to use him as bait \Nso I can see someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.06,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.65,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,You're the one they're after, Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.32,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,That black-haired one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.80,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Okkotsu. Just worry about \Ngetting away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.72,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,He seems like the same type as Satoru Gojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.50,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,You'll die if you fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.43,Italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I shoulda kept quiet about Megumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.75,Italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,That gave me shivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.26,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,It's a plan that keeps Yuji \Nfrom fighting another human
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.20,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,and prevents him from \Nfeeling guilty toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.31,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,He's such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.39,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,We'll meet up at yesterday's spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.67,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.52,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I'll leave that one to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.33,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:32.87,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.77,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,He's this fast with a drawn sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.76,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.03,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I'd planned to crush him \Nwhen he broke into a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.01,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:44.62,Italics,Choso,0,0,0,,I was trying to block Okkotsu's path, \Nbut he read my intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.77,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I was watching earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.08,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,That's Blood Manipulation, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.27,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I don't know why you have it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.03,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Still, it's not that scary, \Naside from Piercing Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.87,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,And producing Piercing \NBlood takes Convergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.34,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,There's a long build-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.56,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I don't need to say any more, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.09,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,It's checkmate. You're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.04,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,You're the one who'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.26,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,Did you think you could \Ngo after my little brother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.08,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,and leave here alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.04,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I'm sure I cut him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.61,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,He's like Maki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.63,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.28,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I don't seem like the power type, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.28,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Even without raw power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.75,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,he has an insane amount of cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.91,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I actually am on the weaker side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:12.07,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,He's enhancing himself with cursed \Nenergy to cover for his lack of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.25,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Everyone does that to some degree, \Nbut when he does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.91,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,The exact opposite of me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.17,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Have you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.19,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I have even more cursed \Nenergy than Gojo-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.20,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,But Sensei has his Six Eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.89,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,so he wastes practically no energy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.79,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,when activating his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.77,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,He's the best there is when \Nit comes to performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.12,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I can run out of cursed energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.71,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,but Sensei can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.75,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Enough chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.19,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.80,Flashback_Italics,Todo,0,0,0,,The better the sorcerer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.18,Flashback_Italics,Todo,0,0,0,,the harder it is to read the \Nflow of their cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.17,Flashback_Italics,Todo,0,0,0,,For a different reason from why yours is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.67,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,315)\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\shad0}When a sorcerer is inexperienced with manipulating cursed energy, there's a deviation in the \Ncursed energy during their preliminary movements, allowing the prediction of their next action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:59.66,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord2\shad0\pos(332,158)\c&H5D3842&\3c&HF7C6E6&}Third-rate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.76,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's because the better a sorcerer is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.68,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}the more precisely they \Nmanipulate cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.92,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,315)\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\shad0}When they have mastered manipulating cursed energy, there is no such deviation in their cursed energy, making it difficult to predict their action until the last second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.92,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord2\shad0\c&H160F10&\3c&HE6AF21&\pos(313.333,171.333)}First-rate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.92,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\an8}That means you can't predict \Ntheir attack until the last second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.18,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,But with this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:10.43,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,There's cursed energy constantly rising \Nfrom his entire body, even his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.08,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's not even a question \Nof reading his movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.18,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,All of his attacks can \Nprove to be decisive blows,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:19.44,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,and he can reduce all damage \Nto the bare minimum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.19,Flashback,Nanami,0,0,0,,You take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.69,Main,Yuji,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't afford to die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.74,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,There are some types
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.54,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,who center their training \Naround the use of a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.48,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,but you don't want to become \Ndependent on a cursed tool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.38,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,and neglect your manipulation \Nof cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.88,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,That's still a ways off for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.26,Flashback,Gojo,0,0,0,,So Slaughter Demon's just \Nan emergency measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.76,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,You never taught me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.10,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,You're putting too much focus into the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:04.94,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,It broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.90,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Well, of course it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.86,Italics,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,He's one of Gojo-sensei's students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:11.13,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I guess you won't go down easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.78,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,The wound's deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.49,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,But none of my organs are falling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.05,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,And now we're both unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.13,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,I can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.74,Main,Rika,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.66,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,We're just playing, Rika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.83,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,"Rika"?! What is this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:35.97,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,A shikigami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.64,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,Where did it come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:40.52,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Hold him still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.27,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.52,Italics,Yuji,0,0,0,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:55.06,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:03.46,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,Itadori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:42.95,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Older brothers who are less competent\Nthan a younger brother serve no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.61,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,...I can't understand how you\Ncould never love your brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:46.74,Main,Okkotsu,0,0,0,,...please report Itadori-kun's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:49.44,Main,Tsukumo,0,0,0,,...all of the distortions may \Nhave started back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.45,Main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:51.41,Main,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,So start by saving me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:52.07,Main,Choso,0,0,0,,It's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:54.58,Main,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Tsumiki has been drawn into this game, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:55.02,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode\N{\fs30}One More Time

